        'My name is Maria Licciardo. Many years ago I introduced my son to karate. I wanted him to have a balance to school. It was important to me then that he rest in himself, which was probably the right way. I am here for each and every one of you. What can I say, not every club has a "Mutti for everything" With us we treat everyone the same, whether large or small.',
